# media is kept local-only for now (~2.6gb, and two videos exceed github's
# 100mb hard per-file limit, so it cannot be committed as-is). the viewer
# references these by relative path, so it works when run locally; on a plain
# github pages deploy the media just shows the "media removed" placeholder.
#
# to host later: upload these folders somewhere (github releases / r2 / a cdn)
# and prepend that base url to the media paths. build scripts: .claude/scripts.

*/avatars/
*/banners/
*/media/
